JOHANNESBURG - Christmas is expensive. An American research company has created a special index based on the song, '12 Days of Christmas'. There's a gift for each of those days. Some are pets, others are musical performances. But one thing's for sure they don't come cheap especially when you're paying in rands. eNCA's Michael Marillier did the maths looking into an American research company's has special index based on the song, '12 Days of Christmas'.